{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
	<div class="container">
		<h1>About Our Recipe App</h1>
		<p>Our Recipe App is a platform where food enthusiasts can share their favorite recipes and discover new ones from others. Whether you're a seasoned chef or a beginner in the kitchen, our app provides a wide variety of recipes for every taste and skill level.</p>

		<h3>Why Our App?</h3>
		<p>We believe that cooking is an art, and sharing your culinary creations with others is a great way to inspire creativity in the kitchen. Our platform allows users to submit their own recipes, get feedback from the community, and explore recipes in various categories.</p>

		<h3>Features</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Browse recipes by category, cuisine, or difficulty level</li>
			<li>Submit your own recipes with step-by-step instructions</li>
			<li>Get cooking tips and tricks from fellow chefs</li>
			<li>Join a community of like-minded food lovers</li>
		</ul>

		<h3>Our Mission</h3>
		<p>Our mission is to create a community-driven platform that connects food lovers and encourages culinary creativity. We want to make cooking fun and accessible for everyone!</p>
	</div>
{% endblock %}
